d] Referral page §2: Stats summary card\n   440→**Status**: Done\n   441→**Changes**:\n   442→- Created `apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralStatsCard.tsx`:\n   443→  - Fetches stats on mount via `getReferralStats(accessToken)` with cancellation guard\n   444→  - Four stat boxes in a grid: Referred Players, Active (7d), Total Volume (SOL), Total Earned (SOL)\n   445→  - `formatSol()` helper: lamports string → SOL with compact display (1.2k, 1M) for large values, 4 decimal places for small\n   446→  - Loading state: skeleton placeholders per stat box (28px height, pulse animation)\n   447→  - Error handling: silently falls back to zeros on fetch failure\n   448→- Updated `ReferralPage.tsx`: imported `ReferralStatsCard`, replaced §2 placeholder comment\n   449→- Added CSS in `index.css`: `.ref-stats-card` styles (card, 4-column grid, JetBrains Mono values, responsive 2-column at 600px)\n   450→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18). Platform typecheck passed. Pre-existing backend typecheck error (HealthDeps) — not introduced by this change.\n   451→\n   452→## Iteration 24 — 2026-03-25T13:26:36Z — OK\n   453→- **Log**: iteration-024.log\n   454→\n   455→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e1866399-0612-4b5c-bae9-0fe08bc8e43b","uuid":"6149c1f0-aa25-442a-b931-7172f5ea4887","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:26:56.627Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/history.md","content":"# Implementation History — 300-referral-system\n\nIteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\nattempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\nof every iteration to understand prior context.\n\n---\n\n## Iteration 1 — 2026-03-24T21:27:27Z — OK\n\n**Item**: [backend] Database migration `011_referral.sql`\n**Status**: Done\n**Changes**:\n- Created `services/backend/migrations/011_referral.sql` with all 5 referral tables:\n  - `referral_codes` — one code per wa