{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ew1UwqLQQVnAjBH54kbdMX","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent. Let me compile the final report with all findings.\n\n## Exploration Findings\n\n### 1. Toast/Notification Patterns\n\n**Files with notification imports:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/quests/components/ChestDropNotification.tsx` — **Active notification pattern**\n\n**Current Pattern:**\nThe platform uses a **custom notification system** via `QuestsContext`:\n- Component: `ChestDropNotification` — renders a toast-like div with inline SVG icon\n- Context: `QuestsContext` provides `chestDropNotification` state with `visible` flag\n- CSS: `.chest-drop-notification`, `.chest-drop-notification__content`, `.chest-drop-notification__icon`, `.chest-drop-notification__text`\n- **No external toast library** (no `react-hot-toast`, `react-toastify`, etc.)\n\n**Referral Integration Gap:**\nIn `useReferralApply.ts` (line 58), there's a TODO comment:\n```typescript\n// TODO: replace with toast notification when toast system is implemented\nconsole.warn(\"[referral] Referral code applied successfully\");\n```\nThe code currently logs to console instead of showing a visible toast.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Referral CSS Classes\n\nLocated in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/index.css` (lines 16633-16875):\n\n**Page & Layout:**\n- `.referral-page` — max-width container, flex column layout\n- `.referral-page__connect` — centered connect-wallet prompt\n- `.referral-page__header` — header section\n- `.referral-page__title` — large title (1.5rem)\n- `.referral-page__subtitle` — dimmed subtitle\n\n**Link Card Components:**\n- `.ref-link-card` — main card wrapper, border + padding\n- `.ref-link-card__title` — section label (uppercase green)\n- `.ref-link-card__desc` — description text\n- `.ref-link-card__skeleton` — pulsing loader\n- `.ref-link-card__form` — flex column gap\n- `.ref-link-card__input-row` — flex input row with prefix\n- `.ref-link-card__prefix` — monospace prefix text\n- `.ref-link-card__input` — transparent input field\n- `.ref-link-card__error` — error text (color-error)\n- `.ref-link-card__actions` — flex button row\n- `.ref-link-card__btn`, `.ref-link-card__btn--primary`, `.ref-link-card__btn--secondary`, `.ref-link-card__btn--copy` — buttons\n- `.ref-link-card__display` — display section\n- `.ref-link-card__url-row` — flex row for URL display\n- `.ref-link-card__url` — monospace URL display (read-only)\n- `.ref-link-card__change` — underlined change link\n\n**Stats Card Components:**\n- `.ref-stats-card` — stats container\n- `.ref-stats-card__title` — uppercase green title\n- `.ref-stats-card__grid` — 4-column grid (2 on mobile)\n- `.ref-stats-card__stat` — flex column stat item\n- `.ref-stats-card__value` — large monospace value\n- `.ref-stats-card__label` — uppercase dimmed label\n- `.ref-stats-card__skeleton` — pulsing loader for stats\n\n---\n\n### 3. Solana Explorer URL Patterns\n\nLocated in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/solana-env.ts`:\n\n**Functions:**\n```typescript\nexport function explorerTxUrl(signature: string): string {\n  const base = `https://explorer.solana.com/tx/${signature}`;\n  return SOLANA_CLUSTER === \"mainnet-beta\"\n    ? base\n    : `${base}?cluster=${SOLANA_CLUSTER}`;\n}\n\nexport function explorerAddressUrl(address: string): string {\n  const base = `https://explorer.solana.com/address/${address}`;\n  return SOLANA_CLUSTER === \"mainnet-beta\"\n    ? base\n    : `${base}?cluster=${SOLANA_CLUSTER}`;\n}\n```\n\n**Usage in ProfileTransactions:**\n```typescript\n<a\n  href={explorerTxUrl(tx.txSig)}\n  target=\"_blank\"\n  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n  className=\"profile-transactions__explorer-link\"\n  title=\"View on Solana Explorer\"\n>\n  &#x2197;\n</a>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. useReferralApply Hook\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/hooks/useReferralApply.ts`\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Watches `isAuthenticated`, `accessToken`, and `address`\n- Reads referral code from `localStorage` under key `\"referral_code\"` (stored as JSON: `{ code: string }`)\n- On first auth after code is stored, auto-calls `applyReferralCode(accessToken, code)`\n- **Permanent failure handling:** Clears storage if error includes: `ALREADY_LINKED`, `SELF_REFERRAL`, `NOT_FOUND`, `INVALID`, or case-insensitive variants\n- **Transient failure handling:** Keeps storage on network errors so retry occurs on next auth\n- **Success:** Clears storage, logs to console (no visible toast yet)\n- Uses `useRef` to prevent duplicate calls within same auth session\n\n---\n\n### Summary for Integration\n\n| Item | Finding |\n|------|---------|\n| **Toast System** | Custom via QuestsContext + ChestDropNotification component; no external library |\n| **Referral CSS** | Complete set of `.ref-*` classes in index.css (lines 16633–16875) |\n| **Explorer Links** | `explorerTxUrl()` and `explorerAddressUrl()` in solana-env.ts; cluster-aware with ?cluster= param for devnet/testnet |\n| **Apply Hook Gap** | `useReferralApply.ts` uses `console.warn()` instead of toast; TODO on line 58 |"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a24c6eb6f9bdbe510 (use SendMessage with to: 'a24c6eb6f9bdbe510' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 49877\ntool_uses: 13\nduration_ms: 28261</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e1866399-0612-4b5c-bae9-0fe08bc8e43b","uuid":"c65bbf48-0fda-41a7-8e14-99b5e4d7464b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:27:56.710Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Quick exploration: \n1. Search for existing toast/notification patterns in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/` — how do they show toasts? What imports/functions are used?\n2. Read the referral-related CSS in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/index.css` — search for `.ref-` or `.referral-` class names and return those 